scene.message:
Nanjo: That's...!!{nl}
Behind it - is that the{nl}
core of the Deva System?!{waitkey}{ret}

Pandora: At last...{nl}
at last you've come so far...{nl}
fushu... rururururururu...{waitkey}{clearbox}This is... the "Gate of{nl}
Paradise" I finally seized...{nl}
I'll give it to no one...{waitkey}{clearbox}With it I'll make a paradise{nl}
- a paradise where nothing{nl}
exists at all...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: No! That's not{nl}
the "Gate of Paradise"!{waitkey}It's "Pandora's Box" -{nl}
the bringer of calamity{nl}
to this world!{waitkey}{ret}

Pandora: Fushururururu...{nl}
All is futile... everything...{nl}
You're futile... I'm futile...{waitkey}{clearbox}I have no need for futile{nl}
things... Vanish from{nl}
existence... Fushuruaaaah!{waitkey}{ret}
